@deftypefun {int} {lw6snd_test} (int @var{mode})
@var{mode}:  0 for check only, 1 for full test

Runs the @code{snd} module test suite. If run in check mode (0),
won't really perform the test, since it could fail because
of hardware problems, context, permissions...

@strong{Return value:}  1 if test is successfull, 0 on error.
@end deftypefun

